channel.title: Gaming Ventrilo
channel.description:
Bored of sitting on the computer and playing that favorite game of yours and nobody to talk to? Well Epic Gaming Ventrilo is here just for that Ventrilo is program where you can voice chat with people around the world. Our vent is centered around online games. Mainly RuneScape but you can still come to our vent no matter what you play! Or if you don't play any games you can come here to chat with your friends. What sets us aside from all the other vents is that we host contests to win a membership in the vent where you have more privileges. We also do prank calls - singing competitions - rap battles, and much, much more.
